        "created_at": "2020-05-06T09:34:11.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"160746\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Other feature seems to be lower levels of alcohol (1 to 1.5 degree less) in 2019 which some will like. Quantities not that high.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>In reds it\u2019s similar or a bit lower to 2019 from what I hear; but in whites, quite a bit higher. Hard to generalize from one domaine to another though.</p>",
