        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"11\" data-topic=\"160746\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>I make just two barrels of Chambolle-Musigny for fun. I\u2019m finding it\u2019s a great way to learn about each new vintage, so it complements my day job rather than distracts from it. My dream retirement project is getting together a few hectares and making my own wine.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>That\u2019s fantastic! TWA should run a promotion: a free bottle with every new subscription. <img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/0/0ff9bfcdb0964982cd3240b6159868fbdf215b1a.gif\" width=\"24\" height=\"18\" alt=\"[cheers.gif]\" title=\"cheers\" class=\"animated\"> Be sure to keep us updated.</p>",
